pr_body:
GSoC'22 had this project as a part which is done by @Nameer-Iqbal-Ansari as a contributor under the mentorship of @zeeshanrafique23.
This [blog](https://medium.com/@n.i.ansari200/gsoc22-a-summer-of-opportunity-95b9b2bb9232) contains the brief explanation of this project.
Reference the README.md to run the simulation of AZADI-II through FuseSoC.
The process consists on three steps.
```
cd azadi-II/
```
```
export AZADI_ROOT=`pwd`
```
```
fusesoc --cores-root=. run --target=sim merl:azadi-II:azadi_sim --cycles=519800 --timeout=8000000 --HEX=$AZADI_ROOT/verif/tests/basic-test/test.hex --ROM_BIN=$AZADI_ROOT/verif/src/post_rom_verilog.rcf
```
